TITLE: McCarthy thanks Trump after House speaker vote: 'He was with me from the beginning'
SUMMARY: House Speaker Kevin McCarthy thanked former President Donald Trump for supporting him through 15 votes for speaker in the House of Representatives.

TITLE: Noem touts South Dakota’s conservative successes ‘can bring hope to the rest of the country’
SUMMARY: Ahead of her inauguration for a second term steering South Dakota, Republican Gov. Kristi Noem says her state’s conservative successes "can bring hope to the rest of the country."

TITLE: Federal court strikes down Trump-era bump stock ban
SUMMARY: A court has ruled against the Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives' ban on bump stocks, finding the agency acted without congressional authorization.

TITLE: Mike Rogers lunges at Matt Gaetz during House speaker voting, other members forced to intervene: video
SUMMARY: A dramatic incident happened in the House chamber late Friday night during the House speaker votes as a Republican member lunged at another member before he was physically restrained.

TITLE: Kevin McCarthy delivers first remarks after winning House Speaker: 'Our nation is worth fighting for'
SUMMARY: House Speaker Kevin McCarthy delivered his first address after winning the position during a 15th and final vote. In his speech, he laid out his legislative priorities.

TITLE: Trump, McConnell, Schumer respond after Kevin McCarthy wins historic, dayslong House Speaker bout
SUMMARY: President Biden, former President Trump and several others congratulated House Speaker Kevin McCarthy after his historic election on Saturday morning.

TITLE: Biden congratulates Kevin McCarthy on winning House speakership following dramatic process
SUMMARY: President Biden swiftly congratulated House Speaker Kevin McCarthy on his victory just after midnight Saturday, which followed several days of deliberations and dramatic votes.

TITLE: Border agents ‘beyond frustrated’ as Biden prepares to finally visit besieged southern border
SUMMARY: Top Border Patrol officials say agents are beyond frustrated ahead of President Biden's visit to the southern border on Sunday, as they try to deal with the two-year crisis.

TITLE: Kevin McCarthy elected House speaker in 15th floor vote after days of high drama
SUMMARY: After a dramatic 1-vote loss late Friday, the House quickly regrouped and elected Kevin McCarthy speaker of the House in an early Saturday morning vote.

TITLE: McCarthy loses by one vote in shocking 14th attempt as furious floor lobbying fails to sway opponents
SUMMARY: Kevin McCarthy lost his 14th attempt to be House speaker by a single vote late Friday night in a nailbiter vote that shocked GOP lawmakers as it unfolded.

TITLE: Ashli Babbitt's mother arrested by Capitol Police during Jan. 6 protest
SUMMARY: The mother of Ashli Babbit was arrested on Friday during a Jan. 6 demonstration in Washington, D.C. and is being accused of traffic violations.

TITLE: Nancy Pelosi cashes in on messy GOP House speaker fight
SUMMARY: Former House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, D-Calif., is using the Republican speaker fight as an opportunity to fundraise as the GOP heads into its 14th ballot to determine the chamber leader.

TITLE: Wisconsin Republican blasts Gaetz for 'dragging' speaker fight out for 'fundraising'
SUMMARY: Wisconsin Republican Rep.-elect Derrick Van Orden torched Rep.-elect Matt Gaetz for "dragging" out the fight for House speaker for "fundraising" off of it.

TITLE: Ron DeSantis activates National Guard amid migrant surge in Florida Keys
SUMMARY: In response to what the state is calling an "alarming flow of migrants" heading into the Florida Keys, Gov. Ron DeSantis has deployed the Florida National Guard.

TITLE: The Hitchhiker’s Guide to what’s going to go down tonight with the speaker’s election
SUMMARY: We don’t know if McCarthy will win on a potential 14th ballot right after the House returns. But Fox is told GOP brass does expect McCarthy to prevail tonight.

TITLE: Embattled Rep.-elect Santos refuses to answer questions about resume lies while promising to support McCarthy
SUMMARY: Rep.-elect George Santos refused to answer questions regarding accusations he lied about his resume while promising to support McCarthy in the House speaker race.

TITLE: 'Struggling' Chicago residents outraged over Lori Lightfoot's decision to house migrants: 'Help my own first'
SUMMARY: Woodlawn residents spoke out Thursday about a Chicago proposal to house migrants from the Texas border at a vacant Chicago Public School building.

TITLE: Biden links 'sick insurrectionists' to death of Capitol Police officer killed by Nation of Islam supporter
SUMMARY: President Biden, while speaking about fallen Capitol Police Officer Billy Evans, blamed 'sick insurrectionists' for his death in a Nation of Islam-linked attack.

TITLE: GOP 'dysfunction' around McCarthy's speaker bid could boost DeSantis' appeal to voters, insiders suggest
SUMMARY: Some political insiders are weighing how the intraparty chaos among Republicans could be tempting voters who are looking ahead to 2024.

TITLE: Byron Donalds invokes Reagan when asked if he trusts Kevin McCarthy
SUMMARY: Byron Donalds quoted Ronald Regan when asked by Fox News Digital Friday if he trusts Kevin McCarthy to lead the GOP as House speaker in the new Congress.
